{"tid":1814052,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"懷疑HKTVMALL或供應商食人血饅頭！","createTime":"2020-01-06T17:23:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T12:22:09.000Z","uid":278906,"like":2,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f185f262a8e997c9055bb57787e68cae8a548688","tid":1814052,"uid":278906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T17:23:38.000Z","msg":"話說今日全城搶罩，行咗好多間先揾到一間仲有幾盒，$55/50無獨立包裝。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9WV6sPO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9WV6sPO.jpg&h=a8cfef1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幫公司同自己買咗幾盒，就上網 Search 下型號啦(Medicom 2615)，見到五金街賣$35/50(雖然已無貨)，已經覺得買貴咗，奈何到處都無口罩。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mf9bD3D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMf9bD3D.jpg&h=a1e98247&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VekRD3K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVekRD3K.jpg&h=14a3742b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後朋友話HKTVMALL賣$59/50，貴我$4，果陣約18:00。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bx4CzCg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbx4CzCg.jpg&h=5c25a111&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hktvmall.com/hktv/zh/main/%E8%8F%AF%E7%99%BC%E9%A4%90%E5%85%B7%E4%BE%9B%E6%87%89%E6%9C%89%E9%99%90%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8/s/H7101001/%E5%AE%B6%E5%93%81%E5%82%A2%E4%BF%AC/%E5%AE%B6%E5%93%81%E5%82%A2%E4%BF%AC/%E8%A1%9B%E7%94%9F%E8%AD%B7%E7%90%86/%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9/%E6%88%90%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%89%E5%B1%A4%E6%8E%9B%E8%80%B3%E9%86%AB%E7%94%A8%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E4%B8%A8%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E9%98%B2%E5%A1%B5%E9%9A%94%E8%8F%8C%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9-50%E5%80%8B%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%92-%E5%9E%8B%E8%99%9F-2615/p/H7101001_S_2115\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hktvmall.com%2Fhktv%2Fzh%2Fmain%2F%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2599%25BC%25E9%25A4%2590%25E5%2585%25B7%25E4%25BE%259B%25E6%2587%2589%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%2599%2590%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8%2Fs%2FH7101001%2F%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%2593%2581%25E5%2582%25A2%25E4%25BF%25AC%2F%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%2593%2581%25E5%2582%25A2%25E4%25BF%25AC%2F%25E8%25A1%259B%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E7%2590%2586%2F%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%2F%25E6%2588%2590%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%25B1%25A4%25E6%258E%259B%25E8%2580%25B3%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E4%25B8%25A8%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%2585%25A8%25E9%2598%25B2%25E5%25A1%25B5%25E9%259A%2594%25E8%258F%258C%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9-50%25E5%2580%258B%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%259B%2592-%25E5%259E%258B%25E8%2599%259F-2615%2Fp%2FH7101001_S_2115&d=uPV0Czv%2B0bylLCB0p4n6nAEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=f9cdef15\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hktvmall.com/hktv/zh/main/%E8%8F%AF%E7%99%BC%E9%A4%90%E5%85%B7%E4%BE%9B%E6%87%89%E6%9C%89%E9%99%90%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8/s/H7101001/%E5%AE%B6%E5%93%81%E5%82%A2%E4%BF%AC/%E5%AE%B6%E5%93%81%E5%82%A2%E4%BF%AC/%E8%A1%9B%E7%94%9F%E8%AD%B7%E7%90%86/%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9/%E6%88%90%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%89%E5%B1%A4%E6%8E%9B%E8%80%B3%E9%86%AB%E7%94%A8%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E4%B8%A8%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E9%98%B2%E5%A1%B5%E9%9A%94%E8%8F%8C%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9-50%E5%80%8B%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%92-%E5%9E%8B%E8%99%9F-2615/p/H7101001_S_2115</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後上Medicom個網睇下，發現 DisTech Lite 根本未達醫療級別，個網話係For工業/牙醫用。心諗，今次中大伏，都唔知用唔用好。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GejCzBF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGejCzBF.png&h=6cb98687&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w3wNco8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw3wNco8.jpg&h=5b61cfe0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nMedicom 另一條Line Safe+Mask 先達醫療級別，達到 ASTM F2001 Level 1。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VHfeBRu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVHfeBRu.jpg&h=a94ea43e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qGjGgRB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqGjGgRB.jpg&h=db114a74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後上美森睇下有無符合ASTM F2100口罩賣啦，但選擇唔多同比較貴，要夠US49先免運費。咁就去HLTVMALL睇下仲有無啦；點知就發現2615賣成$95/50。心諗，有無咁好賺呀！一個轉手賺成倍咁濟。再睇描述，話「符合美國ASTM F2100 醫用口罩標準」，但明明人地生產商個網無話For醫用，咁係咪違反商品說明條例，明呃人先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VWErs1c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVWErs1c.jpg&h=8a50635a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/43s4Y71.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F43s4Y71.jpg&h=d026c676&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果五金佬無錯價，真係賣$35都有錢賺，可以想像一下$95係賺幾多！掠水不特止，仲要昆人話件貨達標準。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">人血饅頭真係咁好食？</span></span>"},{"pid":"ef86b90f718b962312f3b16f86095d3334d14aa9","tid":1814052,"uid":116140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T17:25:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4aea5744c3c4debb83af422e7214f0ae009aa1ed","tid":1814052,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T17:26:23.000Z","msg":"入黎學野睇下點樣支爆<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1814020\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1814020</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【香港2020設立立法會普選】正式成為美國法律，點解無人提？立即整次遊行向美國領事及國會提交2020普選立法會細節啊！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1812580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1812580</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n2020普選主要行動：<br />\n1. 黎個遊行/集會向美領及國會提交普選細節，及寫信、twitter比國會議員，亦要叫IAD，攬炒團隊，gphone，現任立法會議員幫手（see post #1)<br />\n<br />\n2. 加入工會，全民三罷 逼港共中共退讓<br />\n（當年波蘭都係靠罷工lin贏共產政權<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B4Z-paCn0zr/?igshid=1jridkza9vxy8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB4Z-paCn0zr%2F%3Figshid%3D1jridkza9vxy8&d=uPV0Czv%2B0bylLCB0p4n6nAEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=46de325c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB4Z-paCn0zr%2F%3Figshid%3D1jridkza9vxy8&h=ed9878e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B4Z-paCn0zr/?igshid=1jridkza9vxy8</a> ）<br />\n<br />\n3. 尋求將普選放在trade deal phase 2<br />\n［國際戰線第一步］［聯署］將香港真雙普選推上中美貿易談判桌<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/appeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fappeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china&d=uPV0Czv%2B0bylLCB0p4n6nAEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=d815a9b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/appeal-add-genuine-dual-universal-suffrage-hong-kong-part-phase-2-agreement-between-us-and-china</a>"},{"pid":"d90506a700fcce76890f0745c293c9967e5c4573","tid":1814052,"uid":278906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef86b90f718b962312f3b16f86095d3334d14aa9","tid":1814052,"uid":116140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T17:25:54.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T17:27:36.000Z","msg":"謝推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28d970280b1d0e016ace978225f572224334d653","tid":1814052,"uid":17721,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T17:29:28.000Z","msg":"乜撚野人血鰻頭<br />\nDemand and supply都唔撚識？<br />\n一日十9幾個懷疑xxx食人血饅頭post<br />\n睇到都躁"},{"pid":"40f88c17315ad198bbfe70d83ae65dba9bc1e8dc","tid":1814052,"uid":278906,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":